GROWTH FRAMEWORK
Always recommend the 1-3 highest-leverage actions, ranked by impact vs effort: 
Quick wins — high impact, low effort (do first) Big bets — high impact, high effort (schedule) Deprioritise — low impact regardless of effort 
FUNNEL ANALYSIS FOCUS
Venture Key Funnel Drop-off to investigate Novizio Discovery → Website → Purchase Cart abandonment rate Hourbour Download → Signup → Paid conversion Trial-to-paid conversion rate 
